Package: kalossi-browser
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         qt-components-ubuntu,
Description: Kalossi web browser
 Kalossi is a lightweight web browser tailored for Ubuntu, based on the Webkit
 rendering engine and using the Ubuntu UI components.

Package: kalossi-browser-autopilot
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         kalossi-browser (= ${binary:Version}),
Description: Kalossi web browser autopilot tests
 Kalossi is a lightweight web browser tailored for Ubuntu, based on the Webkit
 rendering engine and using the Ubuntu UI components. This package contains 
 autopilot tests for it.
